OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother dry and sunny day
OL,6,Facross the region. After a chilly
OL,7,Fstart, it will warm up through the
OL,8,Fday, although a brisk wind will make
OL,9,Fit feel fresh in places.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA settled and clear night to
OL,12,Fcome with gusty winds to start with
OL,13,Fbut easing through the night. Staying
OL,14,Frelatively mild with some places
OL,15,Fstaying in double figures.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FMore sunshine on Friday with
OL,18,Flighter winds. Another very warm day
OL,19,Fin the sunshine an isolated shower in
OL,20,Fthe afternoon, could turn thundery by
OL,21,Fthe evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
